sequenceDiagram
    participant CO as Compliance Officer
    participant C as Customer
    participant S as Sales Team
    participant F as Finance
    participant IT as IT Ops

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX Doc Gate 1: Request Intake Record
    C->>S: Submit onboarding request
    Note over C,S: 📋 DOC-1: Request Intake Record<br/>(timestamp, customer ID, channel)
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Compliance identity pre-screening before credit check
    S->>CO: Identity pre-screening request
    CO->>CO: Identity Pre-Screening<br/>(KYC/AML verification)
    Note over CO: 🔒 SOX Checkpoint 1
    alt Identity cleared
        CO-->>S: Identity verified – proceed
    else Identity flagged
        CO-->>S: Identity blocked – reject onboarding
        S-->>C: Onboarding denied (identity failure)
    end
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    S->>F: Credit check request

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Risk assessment with RACI annotation + Doc Gate 2
    F->>F: Risk Assessment (Score >750, Verified Co., Clean History?)
    Note over F: 📋 DOC-2: Risk Assessment Record<br/>(score, company status, history)
    Note over S,F: RACI – Risk Assessment:<br/>R: Finance | A: Finance Director<br/>C: Compliance Officer | I: Sales Team
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Compliance validation of risk scoring output
    F->>CO: Risk score validation request
    CO->>CO: Validate Risk Scoring Output<br/>(methodology, data integrity, thresholds)
    Note over CO: 🔒 SOX Checkpoint 2
    CO-->>F: Risk score validated
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    alt Low-Risk (all criteria met) - Expedited Path
        F-->>S: Auto-approved (low-risk, no director approval needed)

        %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - RACI for auto-approval + Doc Gate 3
        Note over S,CO: RACI – Auto-Approval Decision:<br/>R: Finance | A: Finance Director<br/>C: Compliance Officer | I: Sales Team
        Note over F: 📋 DOC-3: Approval Justification<br/>(auto-approved, low-risk rationale)
        %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

        S->>IT: Provision accounts (expedited)

        %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Compliance access control review after provisioning
        IT->>CO: Access control review request (expedited)
        CO->>CO: Access Control Review<br/>(least privilege, role mapping, segregation of duties)
        Note over CO: 🔒 SOX Checkpoint 3
        Note over IT,CO: 📋 DOC-4: Audit Log<br/>(accounts provisioned, permissions granted, reviewer)
        CO-->>IT: Access controls verified
        %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

        IT-->>C: Welcome email + credentials (within 24h)

    else High-Risk (any criteria failed) - Standard Path
        F->>F: Escalate to Finance Director
        F-->>S: Finance Director Approval (24h SLA)

        %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - RACI for director approval + Doc Gate 3
        Note over S,CO: RACI – Director Approval Decision:<br/>R: Finance Director | A: CFO<br/>C: Compliance Officer | I: Sales Team
        Note over F: 📋 DOC-3: Approval Justification<br/>(director-approved, high-risk rationale, conditions)
        %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

        S->>IT: Provision accounts (standard)

        %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Compliance access control review after provisioning
        IT->>CO: Access control review request (standard)
        CO->>CO: Access Control Review<br/>(least privilege, role mapping, segregation of duties)
        Note over CO: 🔒 SOX Checkpoint 3
        Note over IT,CO: 📋 DOC-4: Audit Log<br/>(accounts provisioned, permissions granted, reviewer)
        CO-->>IT: Access controls verified
        %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

        IT-->>C: Welcome email + credentials
    end

    C->>IT: First login confirmation
    IT->>S: Onboarding complete

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - RACI for onboarding closure + Doc Gate 5
    Note over S,CO: RACI – Onboarding Closure:<br/>R: Sales Team | A: Sales Manager<br/>C: Compliance Officer | I: Customer
    Note over S,CO: 📋 DOC-5: Closure Record<br/>(completion date, all checkpoints passed,<br/>audit trail reference, SOX sign-off)
    CO->>CO: Final SOX compliance sign-off
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    S->>C: Kickoff meeting scheduled

%% EXPLANATION:
%% Added a Compliance Officer participant positioned at the top of the diagram with three SOX checkpoints: (1) an identity pre-screening gate before the credit check that can block onboarding for KYC/AML failures, (2) a risk scoring validation step after Finance completes its assessment to verify methodology and data integrity, and (3) an access control review after account provisioning in both the expedited and standard paths to enforce least-privilege and segregation of duties. Five documentation gates were added as notes attached to their source interactions: DOC-1 at request intake, DOC-2 at risk assessment output, DOC-3 at approval justification (in both paths), DOC-4 as audit logs after provisioning, and DOC-5 as a closure record with final SOX sign-off. RACI annotations were added at every major decision point (risk assessment, auto-approval, director approval, and onboarding closure). All original business logic—the risk-based routing, expedited vs. standard paths, and post-provisioning steps—remains unchanged.